{"tid":2341100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到條街咁多人， 陳雲同佢d狗都吠少幾聲","createTime":"2020-12-26T05:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T05:49:38.000Z","uid":197783,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5da6301519778fc5d8317b675c8c7689c0b576d","tid":2341100,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，打稻草人，恐懼撚丫嘛。<br />\n<br />\n晨早我就屌鳩你地熱狗班老母臭閪架啦。<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩只係香港人自私怕死，屌你個傻根老母臭閪，成日扯埋極權黎講，講撚左成年，一到節日長假期就收撚你皮啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節日得返傻根起屋企自我隔離，全部恐懼撚都出哂街食飯慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bcf46ed7f6414bb468de2919118bdc37700b9a","tid":2341100,"uid":49151,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"其實香港人唔驚 得連登仔驚武肺姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6372c667d0dea961c1aa4231058a6637b246042","tid":2341100,"uid":197783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7bcf46ed7f6414bb468de2919118bdc37700b9a","tid":2341100,"uid":49151,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"其實香港人唔驚 得連登仔驚武肺姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"廢青、隱青同傻根一樣果班人，乜閪都驚架啦，就算同佢講世界末日都驚一餐架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論係信得熱狗青城都唔係正常人，正常人依一年除左冇得去旅行，同唔食美心蛋糕，其他野根本生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29efe844df82289360cca1acfd634afdd0a4e16e","tid":2341100,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"